## 📁 Project Structure

includes/       → header files  
src/            → source files  
textures/       → game images (.xpm)  
maps/           → test maps  
get_next_line/  → file reading  
ft_printf/      → custom printf  
minilibx-linux/ → graphics library  

---

## 🎯 Notes

- The player cannot exit before collecting all collectibles  
- The game closes when ESC is pressed or window is closed  
- Each move is counted and printed in the terminal  

